    end

    Runtime --> TTL

    TTL --> Rotation
    Rotation --> Refresh
    Refresh --> Resolve

    Runtime --> Cleanup
    Agent --> Cleanup

    %% =====================================================
    %% Security Controls
    %% =====================================================

    subgraph Security["Security Controls"]

        MTLS["Mutual TLS"]

