    end

    Validate --> LeastPrivilege
    Resolve --> MTLS
    Decrypt --> Encryption

    Inject --> Audit
    Rotation --> Audit
    Cleanup --> Audit

    Audit --> Events

    %% =====================================================
    %% Failure Handling
    %% =====================================================

    subgraph Failure["Resolution Failure"]

        Missing["Missing Secret"]

        Unauthorized["Access Denied"]

        ProviderDown["Provider Unavailable"]

        Retry["Retry Logic"]

        FailDeployment["Fail Deployment"]

    end

